OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778850694
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FA student has died, and two other
OL,7,Fyoung people are being treated
OL,8,Ffollowing an outbreak of meningitis in
OL,9,FReading.
OL,11,FOne of the cases has been confirmed as
OL,12,Fmeningitis B (MenB), which was linked
OL,13,Fto a cluster of fatal cases in Kent
OL,14,Fearlier this year.
OL,16,FHowever, this outbreak is not same
OL,17,Fstrain of MenB that was seen in
OL,18,FCanterbury in March, and the UK Health
OL,19,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) is currently
OL,20,Fcarrying out further testing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
