OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FThe student who died was a student at
OL,7,Fthe Henley College in Oxfordshire,
OL,8,Fwhilst the other two confirmed cases
OL,9,Fattended schools in Reading.
OL,11,FWhich schools have confirmed cases of
OL,12,Fmeningitis?
OL,14,FSo far, the UKHSA says three schools
OL,15,Fhave pupils who have tested positive
OL,16,Ffor the disease.
OL,18,FOne of those is the Henley College,
OL,19,Fwhich offers A-levels and vocational
OL,20,Fcourses to teenagers in sixth form.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
