CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778850694
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FThe other two cases are both in the
OL,7,FReading area. One person attended the
OL,8,FReading Blue Coat School, which is an
OL,9,Findependent school in the Sonning
OL,10,Farea. It teaches children and
OL,11,Fteenagers from ages 11 to 18.
OL,13,FThe other young person was a student
OL,14,Fat Highdown School and Sixth Form
OL,15,FCentre in the Emmer Green area.
OL,17,FWhat is the advice for young people
OL,18,Fand parents at schools with confirmed
OL,19,Fmeningitis cases?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
