PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778850694
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FThe UKHSA says the risk to the wider
OL,7,Fpublic 'remains low', but students and
OL,8,Fparents at affected schools are being
OL,9,Freminded of the symptoms of meningitis.
OL,11,FClose contacts of pupils who have
OL,12,Fmeningitis have already been offered
OL,13,Fantibiotics, which the UKHSA says is a
OL,14,Fprecautionary measure.
OL,16,FStudents should continue to attend
OL,17,Fschool as usual.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
