OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778850694
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FReading Borough Council, which
OL,7,Foversees schools and colleges in
OL,8,FReading, told ITV Meridian it is
OL,9,Fworking closely with the UKHSA and the
OL,10,Flocal NHS.
OL,12,FIt says people may be feeling anxious,
OL,13,Fbut stressed meningitis B 'does not
OL,14,Fspread easily'. However, it is urging
OL,15,Fresidents to seek health advice if
OL,16,Fthey feel unwell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
