PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778850694
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,F"Someone with meningitis or sepsis can
OL,7,Fbecome seriously unwell very quickly.
OL,8,FResidents should call 999 or go to
OL,9,Ftheir nearest A&E immediately if they
OL,10,Fsuspect they or someone they care for
OL,11,Fhas meningitis or sepsis. If they are
OL,12,Funsure, residents can seek advice
OL,13,Fthrough NHS 111 online or by calling
OL,14,FNHS 111."
